{
  "stem": "9943.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But this teacher, [NON-ENGLISH], was teaching us Polish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was clear that we are not going to be able to, to continue education if we stay in our little shtetl.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we-- my, my mother went, went to-- a couple of times to Luck where her parents lived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they started to look where we should settle, and-- and what they should do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in the meantime, I got reacquainted with this, this little town of Wlodzimierzec, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with the group of girls and, and boys who were our own age.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So again, life went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then we settled in a town, which was called Volodymyr-Volynskyi.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now Volodymyr, it's like your old 'Volodymyr-itz'-- Wlodzimierzec.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, you see, I'm mixing already the names from Russian to Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in Volodymyr-Volynskyi, that's where we went to gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where we got settled.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was Poland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now we are back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We left Russia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We left the, the, the Reds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we had the Whites because the Whites were a long time in Rostov.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Relatively speaking, it took longer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]-- I remember the names of the generals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember the-- I was reading papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember that Wilson and Lloyd George and Poincare what-- they were all that-- because they [INAUDIBLE] have discussions in the house about it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in Wlodzimierz, we spent another year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First it was a year in, in Wlodzimierzec, and then a year in Wlodzimierz in order to-- to catch up, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] catch up with, with both, with their schooling and the language.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have to tell you that the-- that the time in Rostov in gymnasium, [INAUDIBLE] we did not have too much of studying going on, serious study.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
